{"tid":543790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"金拱門扭扭粉冇得加芝士啊！","createTime":"2018-01-29T00:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T01:03:09.000Z","uid":23339,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0085d1c82441ce750a35e2a38babd2f25bfd5a2f","tid":543790,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T00:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇曬生存意義。"},{"pid":"a7bf93e01d07d8ec1d5fd8daede09f4d15efa7cb","tid":543790,"uid":23339,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T00:54:20.000Z","msg":"你諗下，在星期一至五繁忙的早上，<br />\n麥......唔係，金拱門嘅早餐拯救了幾多起早貪黑嘅香港打工仔。<br />\n<br />\n佢地默默耕耘，<br />\n為呢個社會嘅發展做出無法計算嘅建設與貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n陪伴住佢地一日之際開始嘅，<br />\n就正正是金拱門的早餐。<br />\n<br />\n扭扭粉佢雖然唔係話特別好食，但對於啱啱起身嘅人黎講，<br />\n一碗熱騰騰嘅扭扭粉有雞蛋有火腿扒係比人嘅幾咁溫暖嘅感覺。<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，<br />\n那就是媽媽的味道。<br />\n<br />\n在繁忙的早上，令你精神充沛。<br />\n保持最好嘅狀態去開始你一日嘅工作。<br />\n<br />\n加塊車打芝士，那濃郁經發酵過的奶香味，<br />\n可以令到佢嘅味道昇華，並可以令人吸收到更加多嘅能量以及營養。<br />\n<br />\n那正正是打工仔所需要且不可缺少嘅能量。<br />\n<br />\n扭扭粉，係唔可以冇咗芝士。"},{"pid":"d7ae33a0b234be7e926be86703fe512be394599b","tid":543790,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T00:54:47.000Z","msg":"擺食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ae5f694e8b9732b1239e5c412f3b49074622c9a","tid":543790,"uid":30235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T00:55:19.000Z","msg":"月頭就冇咗啦"},{"pid":"10e1c24a9fb73c3199ff026b312f614477581cec","tid":543790,"uid":23339,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T00:57:30.000Z","msg":"BTW 我加多咗個包用佢個芝士掉落去扭扭粉解決曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n店員笑咗，我都笑咗。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋笑我on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我笑佢哋睇唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/29/085517_a841bea9d67ebce519807bcdc05f7a45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F29%2F085517_a841bea9d67ebce519807bcdc05f7a45.jpg&h=25367117&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f2d509e022536e3c98dc30f09051033bab9180b","tid":543790,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7ae33a0b234be7e926be86703fe512be394599b","tid":543790,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T00:54:47.000Z","msg":"擺食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T00:58:12.000Z","msg":"我嘅精神食糧黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284019c48be707be4de065a11e9c846106201d07","tid":543790,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ae5f694e8b9732b1239e5c412f3b49074622c9a","tid":543790,"uid":30235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T00:55:19.000Z","msg":"月頭就冇咗啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"好耐冇食過佢個早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366a7116e01a66e20f723c3d384b644c37d81ebd","tid":543790,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T01:03:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}